{"tid":639010,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"魚缸d水好污濁 之後d魚就白色一點點 可以點醫","createTime":"2018-04-23T07:31:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T21:39:39.000Z","uid":47839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1adb3fded422d839a7e04f5587e7347c2862191c","tid":639010,"uid":47839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T07:31:50.000Z","msg":"我買左個長42 闊30 高32既魚缸<br />\n大概養左兩個禮拜多d <br />\n有買過濾器<br />\n但前幾日換完水冇耐 <br />\n之後d魚就白色一點點 同水好污濁<br />\n<br />\n我想有咩方法可以救佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/153000_ba17e41682eee0e2d938f3a46c1cb80a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F153000_ba17e41682eee0e2d938f3a46c1cb80a.png&h=949e3ac3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/153005_e1935d59180912c69982ba2fe60b9731.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F153005_e1935d59180912c69982ba2fe60b9731.png&h=24f7b267&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/153014_d7a9ddd07e56ab88a14ac70fa728eab6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F153014_d7a9ddd07e56ab88a14ac70fa728eab6.png&h=718827d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cfb1b971fe1388d3a4ce74335c32bffee10094ef","tid":639010,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T07:34:04.000Z","msg":"無開缸直接隊晒d野落去養?"},{"pid":"4aab6f00ec33767027b4ee93bcfa63bfd69e445f","tid":639010,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T07:38:02.000Z","msg":"無養水咁大個缸？<br />\n生水霉啦條魚，有無第二個魚缸用住隔夜水落藥醫條魚先"},{"pid":"495989d454fe9ede0625fc03f6023961336b8856","tid":639010,"uid":653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T07:38:31.000Z","msg":"同埋咁大個缸得舊咁既過濾<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5b6269ca23477d5b4bf1707f351ce25c9c26b0b","tid":639010,"uid":47839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfb1b971fe1388d3a4ce74335c32bffee10094ef","tid":639010,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T07:34:04.000Z","msg":"無開缸直接隊晒d野落去養?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T07:38:46.000Z","msg":"我有個朋友個親戚養開魚<br />\n咁岩佢話換魚缸<br />\n所以我就平平d買左佢個缸養<br />\n所以我就咁放左落去養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪咁樣就出事"},{"pid":"d907238d9ccc0bd0698e6e4be83fb22f203b361b","tid":639010,"uid":15027,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T07:39:24.000Z","msg":"養下水先車d水入缸<br />\n<br />\n換個好少少嘅過濾<br />\n<br />\n白點係因為你缸水水質有問題<br />\n管理返好d就會無事<br />\n嚴重嘅出魚街買藥"},{"pid":"2dea6c176c37fe8cd90681c9edc116c429e00fc2","tid":639010,"uid":47839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"495989d454fe9ede0625fc03f6023961336b8856","tid":639010,"uid":653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T07:38:31.000Z","msg":"同埋咁大個缸得舊咁既過濾<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T07:39:41.000Z","msg":"姐係個過濾器太廢 ？"},{"pid":"93cf557ef5bc3e7597c13e606f849bbba3e7d210","tid":639010,"uid":47839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d907238d9ccc0bd0698e6e4be83fb22f203b361b","tid":639010,"uid":15027,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T07:39:24.000Z","msg":"養下水先車d水入缸<br />\n<br />\n換個好少少嘅過濾<br />\n<br />\n白點係因為你缸水水質有問題<br />\n管理返好d就會無事<br />\n嚴重嘅出魚街買藥"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T07:43:02.000Z","msg":"養水可唔可以用水喉水？"},{"pid":"92960ca81368d53569d1f492a0f0c196a5a89f82","tid":639010,"